high_descs: Turn left and then turn left again once passing the table, entering the room with the bed.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Go towards the bread at the foot of the bed.
Slice the bread with the knife.
Exit the room the way you came in, turn left, then keep going until you can turn left to go into the shelf.
Place the knife down on the shelf.
Leave the room the way you came in, turn right and go straight until you can turn right to get back to the bed.
Pick up a slice of bread from the bed.
Exit the room the way you came in, then go straight and left to the kitchen area, where the microwave is.
Use the microwave on the slice of bread.
Go to the fridge to the right of the microwave.
Place the slice of bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Slice some bread, microwave one slice and place it in a fridge.

high_descs: Walk through the hallway and go to the bed.
Pick up the knife that is on the bed.
Take the knife and slice the bread.
turn around and walk out of the room.
walk down the hallway until you get to a door which has a little open way in the bottom.
Put the knife in the little opening in the shelf.
Turn around and go to the bedroom using the bed.
Pick up a slice of bread from the bed.
Take the bread and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the bread to heat up.
Take the bread out of the microwave and walk toward the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the slice of bread in it.
anns.task_desc: Preparing bread to put in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left to walk up to the floor lamp and turn left to reach the bedroom and face the bed on the left.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Move right to face the bread on the bed.
Cut the bread into slices with the knife.
Turn right and exit the room, take a left turn to walk down the passage and turn left to enter the shelf.
Put the knife on the shelf in the closet on the right.
Turn around and turn right to walk down the passage and take a right turn to enter the bedroom and face the bed.
Pick up the slice of bread from the bed.
Turn around to exit the room and walk till the floor lamp and turn left to reach the microwave.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave to heat and take it out.
Turn right to face the fridge.
Put the bread slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Bread in the Fridge.
